#: quill/ui/ai_hub_dialog.py:1192
msgid ""
"Data sent to cloud AI providers\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"When cloud AI is enabled, QUILL sends your document text or selection to "
"the provider you configured (e.g. OpenAI, Claude). The following "
"operations send data:\n"
"\n"
"  - Ask Quill chat\n"
"  - Rewrite, Summarize, Expand, Grammar check, Spell check\n"
"  - AI Translate (when using AI provider, not LibreTranslate)\n"
"  - AI Thesaurus\n"
"  - Document Q&A\n"
"  - TTS Read Aloud (text only, no document metadata)\n"
"  - Transcribe / Translate Audio (audio file bytes)\n"
"\n"
"QUILL never sends your API key to any service other than the configured "
"provider, never tracks usage, and never stores responses externally."
msgstr ""
"Dati inviati ai provider cloud IA\n"
"--------------------------------\n"
"Quando il cloud IA è attivo, QUILL invia il testo  del documento o la "
"selezione al provider che hai configurato (es. OpenAI, Claude). Le "
"seguenti operazioni inviano dati:\n"
"\n"
"  - Chiedi a Quill Chat\n"
